title: George Benson doesn´t believe allegations against Michael Jackson
description:
4:09 "...and the Michael Jackson I knew was a man like me who knocks on doors with a bible in his hand. Gee, that´s not a guy who ..all the things they were saying. Remember they said Prince died of drugs as if he was a drug user. That´s completely different than the man I knew..."
They start talking about Michael at min 3:10.
Singer George Benson who was friends with Michael Jackson talks music history – and why he doesn’t believe the allegations against Michael Jackson
George Benson is interviewed by British Channel 4 News on July 5, 2019
